{
    "title": "Seu Olhar",
    "artist": "Ceumar",
    "composer": "Arnaldo Antunes / Paulo Tatit",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span> \n \n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A/G\">A/G</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu olhar lá fora, o seu olhar no céu </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#º\">C#º</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu olhar demora, o seu olhar no meu </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm/Bb\">Bm/Bb</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/A\">D/A</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/G#\">E/G#</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu olhar, o seu olhar melhora, melhora o meu </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A/G\">A/G</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Onde a brasa mora e devora o breu </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#º\">C#º</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Como a chuva molha o que se escondeu </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm/Bb\">Bm/Bb</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/A\">D/A</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/G#\">E/G#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu olhar , o seu olhar melhora, melhora o meu </span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span> )\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span> )\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm/Bb\">Bm/Bb</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/A\">D/A</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/G#\">E/G#</span> )\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A/G\">A/G</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu olhar agora, o seu olhar nasceu </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#º\">C#º</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu olhar me olha, o seu olhar é seu </span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm/Bb\">Bm/Bb</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/A\">D/A</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E/G#\">E/G#</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O seu olhar, seu olhar melhora, melhora o meu</span>\n",
